body: I sort of expect her to get caught though, she’s portrayed as being impulsive. The more she does it, the sloppier she’ll get with hiding stuff and then get caught. Lol, what has hentai done to me 😂

Damn, the cheating story in page 331 is better than most. This one it’s the woman who pursues another guy who is reluctant to cheat. And she tries to assuage her guilt with all these stupid lines. Even the guy gets disgusted with her and refuses to use her first name and sticks to using her family name. Kinda wish she got caught like the girl from Furatsu Sensei’s other work.
I had no idea E-musu Aki Sensei died.... I’m truly shocked. Was just reading his While Big Brother’s Away yesterday and marvelling at the art and the beautiful way he drew eyebrows... so sad. 😢
